text: Urs Steinemann (born 1 February 1959) is a Swiss rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Switzerland Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
